title: Klobas/Kesecker Ensemble Kicks Off CSUEB Music Department Season (California State University, East Bay)
text: ( Source : California State University, East Bay ) CSUEB music department faculty member Pat Klobas plays double bass for the Klobas/Kesecker Ensemble . Cal State East Bay 's music department will kick off its season with a faculty jazz recital
